Playbook recommendation and management

Usage: do-memory-cli playbook <COMMAND>

Commands:
  recommend  Generate a playbook for a task
  explain    Explain a pattern in human-readable form
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
